<h1>Your offer is live</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @offer.name %>,</p>

<p>Thanks a lot for using HopHub!</p>

<p>Your offer for the event "<strong><%= @offer.event.name %></strong>" has been confirmed and is now active and visible here:</p>

<p><a href="<%= event_offer_url(@offer.event, @offer) %>" class="button">View your offer</a></p>

<% if @notified_count.to_i > 0 %>
  <p><%= t('mail.offer.confirmed.notified', count: @notified_count) %></p>
<% end %>

<p>If you want to edit or delete your offer, please use the following secret link. Please keep this link to yourself and do not share it with others:</p>

<div class="secret-link"><a href="<%= edit_event_offer_url(@offer.event, @offer, token: @offer.token, locale: I18n.locale) %>"><%= edit_event_offer_url(@offer.event, @offer, token: @offer.token, locale: I18n.locale) %></a></div>

<p>Your offer will automatically be deleted after the date you set, or when the event ends.</p>

<p>Happy sharing, you are awesome!</p>

<p class="signoff">Kind regards from the HopHub platform.</p>
